msgstr "Activer une taille adaptative d'étiquette "

#: contents/ui/settings/EditorHighlightPreview.qml:25
#, kde-format
msgctxt ""
"@description:checkbox, a Markdown tag, e.g: the `#` for a header `# this is "
"header`, similar concept as an html tag `<h1>`"
msgid "The adaptive size will scale the tag size based on its surrounding."
msgstr ""
"La taille adaptative mettra à l'échelle la taille de l'étiquette en fonction "
"de son environnement."

